{
  "_comment": "Default time-sensitive rule list for the response cache freshness gate. Single source of truth — seed.ts UPSERTs this into semantic_cache_config.time_sensitive_overrides on a fresh DB; AIGW pulls it via Hub shadow. Both RequireQuestionMark and RequireEntity default to false: keyword strength carries the signal. Editing this file changes the on-DB defaults for newly-seeded clusters; existing clusters keep whatever the admin has saved.",
